snippet.title: Cubio - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Cubio is a sandbox game creation platform game developed by 01Studio. Players can create content and make their first game creations without code knowledge using easy-to-use tools and customizable avatars. The projects can be developed alone or together with other creatives before being shared with the community. Cubio is launching at a later date with an alpha releasing soon for PC.

#GameTrailers #Gaming #Cubio
